description: Dominic Pacifico is DJing an upcoming party at the Next Door shoot house. An extravaganza to end all monster bashes, he's just setting up when the A/V guy comes in to do his job. But this isn't no ordinary video expert. No sir. Hired on this job is none other than Cody Cummings, cable guy extraordinaire. No one better at handling your cables. Well before too long wires aren't the only thing making a connection, if you know what I mean, and it turns out, Dominic isn't so bad at handling cable himself.  Enjoy!
title: Pull On My Cable
